CREATE ALGORITHM = UNDEFINED DEFINER = ``root``@``localhost`` SQL SECURITY DEFINER VIEW ``config``.``vw_pipeline_list`` AS

SELECT DISTINCT ``config``.``vw_object_list``.``login_id`` AS ``login_id``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``id`` AS ``id``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``project_id`` AS ``project_id``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``pipeline_name`` AS ``pipeline_name``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``pipeline_cd`` AS ``pipeline_cd``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``pipeline_description`` AS ``pipeline_description``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``pipeline_sequence`` AS ``pipeline_sequence``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``is_active`` AS ``is_active``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``created_by`` AS ``created_by``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``created_dttm`` AS ``created_dttm``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``updated_by`` AS ``updated_by``
	,``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``updated_dttm`` AS ``updated_dttm``
	,``al``.``last_run_id`` AS ``last_run_id``
	,(
		CASE 
			WHEN (``al``.``audit_value`` IS NULL)
				THEN 'New'
			WHEN (``al``.``audit_value`` = 'COMPLETED')
				THEN 'Success'
			WHEN (``al``.``audit_value`` LIKE 'FAILED%')
				THEN 'Failed'
			WHEN (``al``.``audit_value`` = 'NOT STARTED')
				THEN 'Failed'
			ELSE 'Running'
			END
		) AS ``audit_value``
	,(json_unquote(json_extract(``jt``.``option_info``, '$.read')) collate utf8mb4_unicode_ci) AS ``option_read``
	,(json_unquote(json_extract(``jt``.``option_info``, '$.write')) collate utf8mb4_unicode_ci) AS ``option_write``
	,(json_unquote(json_extract(``jt``.``option_info``, '$.execute')) collate utf8mb4_unicode_ci) AS ``option_execute``
FROM (
	(
		(
			(
				``config``.``tbl_pipeline`` JOIN ``config``.``vw_object_list`` ON ((``config``.``vw_object_list``.``object_id`` = ('pipeline_id' collate utf8mb4_unicode_ci)))
				) JOIN json_table(``config``.``vw_object_list``.``option_list``, '$[*]' columns(``option_info`` json path '$')) ``jt`` ON (true)
			) LEFT JOIN (
			SELECT cast(``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``pipeline_id`` AS unsigned) AS ``pipeline_id``
				,``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``taskorpipeline_name`` AS ``job_name``
				,``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``run_id`` AS ``last_run_id``
				,``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``audit_type`` AS ``audit_type``
				,``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``audit_value`` AS ``audit_value``
				,``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``process_dttm`` AS ``process_dttm``
				,rank() OVER (
					PARTITION BY ``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``pipeline_id`` ORDER BY ``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``.``process_dttm`` DESC
					) AS ``status_rank``
			FROM ``config``.``tbl_etl_audit``
			) ``al`` ON ((``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``id`` = ``al``.``pipeline_id``))
		) LEFT JOIN ``config``.``tbl_task`` ON ((``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``id`` = ``config``.``tbl_task``.``pipeline_id``))
	)
WHERE (
		(``config``.``tbl_pipeline``.``pipeline_name`` = json_unquote(json_extract(``jt``.``option_info``, '$.name')))
		AND (json_unquote(json_extract(``jt``.``option_info``, '$.read')) <> 0)
		AND (
			(``al``.``status_rank`` = 1)
			OR (``al``.``status_rank`` IS NULL)
			)
		)
